se">http://india.blogs.nytimes.com/2013/01/03/accused-in-delhi-gang-rape-case-expected-in-court/</guid><dc:creator>By NIHARIKA MANDHANA</dc:creator></item><item><atom:link href="http://www.nytimes.com/2013/01/04/world/asia/us-drone-strike-is-said-to-kill-a-top-pakistani-militant.html?partner=rss&amp;emc=rss" rel="standout" /><title>U.S. Drone Strike Is Said to Kill a Top Pakistani Militant</title><link>http://www.nytimes.com/2013/01/04/world/asia/us-drone-strike-is-said-to-kill-a-top-pakistani-militant.html?partner=rss&amp;emc=rss</link><description>The death of Maulvi Nazir, reported by security officials, was seen as a serious blow to Taliban fighters who attack United States and allied forces in neighboring Afghanistan.&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='http://rss.nytimes.com/c/34625/f/642565/s/272555b1/mf.gif' border='0'/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a href="http://da.feedsportal.com/r/151884206041/u/0/f/642565/c/34625/s/272555b1/a2.htm"&gt;&lt;img src="http://da.feedsportal.com/r/151884206041/u/0/f/642565/c/34625/s/272555b1/a2.img" border="0"/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;img width="1" height="1" src="http://pi.feedsportal.com/r/151884206041/u/0/f/642565/c/34625/s/272555b1/a2t.img" border="0"/&gt;</description><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_geo">Pakistan</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/mdes">Afghanistan War (2001- )</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_org_all">Taliban</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_geo">Waziristan (Pakistan)</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/des">Drones (Pilotless Planes)</category><category domain="http://www.nytimes.com/namespaces/keywords/nyt_per">Nazir, Maulvi</category><pubDate>Thu, 03 Jan 2013 07:49:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.nytimes.com/2013/01/04/world/asia/us-drone-strike-is-said-to-kill-a-top-pakistani-militant.html</guid><dc:creato